WebRTC:
  camera without user intercation: WebRTC (current cordova In-App-Browser doesn't support WebRTC, so you have to use Crosswalk)
  add to android manifest:
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO" />
    MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.CAMERA" />
  https://stackoverflow.com/questions/28934014/getusermedia-android-webview-ionic
